@startuml
title Siemens U273 Plugin - Audio Callback Sequence

actor "DAW Host" as Host
participant "PluginProcessor" as Processor
participant "ParameterBridge" as Params
participant "U273DspEngine" as DSP
participant "MeterBridge" as Meters

Host -> Processor : prepareToPlay(sampleRate, maxBlock)
Processor -> DSP : prepare(config)
DSP --> Processor : preallocated / ready

loop each audio callback
  Host -> Processor : processBlock(buffer, midi)
  Processor -> Params : readSnapshot()
  Params --> Processor : ParameterSnapshot
  alt snapshot valid and DSP prepared
    Processor -> DSP : process(buffer, snapshot)
    DSP -> Meters : publish(MeterFrame)
    DSP --> Processor : audio processed
  else invalid state
    Processor -> Processor : bounded bypass / clear unsafe channels
  end
  Processor --> Host : return before deadline
end

note right of DSP
Forbidden in process:
- allocation
- locks
- logging
- file/network I/O
- unbounded Newton/MNA
end note

@enduml

